18struct VP9Common;
19
20typedef struct TileInfo {

23} TileInfo;
24

26// 'cm->log2_tile_(rows|cols)' & 'cm->mi_(rows|cols)'

28 int col);
29
30void vp9_tile_set_row(TileInfo *tile, const struct VP9Common *cm, int row);
31void vp9_tile_set_col(TileInfo *tile, const struct VP9Common *cm, int col);
32
33void vp9_get_tile_n_bits(int mi_cols, int *min_log2_tile_cols,
34 int *max_log2_tile_cols);

37} // extern "C"
